The '''82nd parallel north''' is a [[circle of latitude]] that is 82 [[degree (angle)|degrees]] [[true north|north]] of the [[Earth|Earth's]] [[equator|equatorial plane]], in the [[Arctic]]. It passes through the [[Arctic Ocean]] and [[North America]].

==Around the world==
