==England== Some of the [[hundred (county division)|hundred]]s and wapentakes in [[England]] (both historic subdivisions of the [[historic counties of England|historic counties]]) were subdivided into divisions. Also a number of the [[Wards of the City of London]] are, or were, divided into two divisions.
